<div
  style="background: rgb(255, 253, 214); color: rgb(30, 30, 30); padding: 1rem 0.5rem; text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;"
>
  Este site está em redesign aberto, então se parecer estranho, é por isso.
</div>
<header class="wrapper region repel" style="--region-space: 1.5rem;" id="main-nav">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mx-auto px-4 py-3 container">
    <a class="u-url" data-variant="naked" href="/">
      <img
        src="/assets/images/pulis.webp"
        alt=""
        srcset=""
        style="max-width: 100%; width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%;"
      />
    </a>

    <form class="hidden sm:block ml-auto" role="search" aria-label="Site" action="/search/" method="get">
      <label class="sr-only" for="q">Search</label>
      <input id="q" name="q" type="search" placeholder="Search…" class="px-3 py-2 border rounded w-64" />
    </form>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 ml-2">
      <button
        id="dark-toggle"
        class="px-2 py-1 border rounded text-sm"
        aria-pressed="false"
        aria-label="Switch to dark mode"
      >
        🌙
      </button>
      <div class="relative">
        <button
          id="a11y-toggle"
          class="px-2 py-1 border rounded text-sm"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="a11y-menu"
        >
          A11y
        </button>
        <div
          id="a11y-menu"
          class="hidden right-0 absolute space-x-2 bg-[var(--surface)] mt-1 p-2 border rounded text-sm whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          <button id="font-dec" class="px-2 py-1 border rounded">A-</button>
          <button id="font-inc" class="px-2 py-1 border rounded">A+</button>
          <button id="contrast-toggle" class="px-2 py-1 border rounded">Contrast</button>
          <button id="motion-toggle" class="px-2 py-1 border rounded">Reduce motion</button>
          <button
            id="font-toggle"
            type="button"
            aria-pressed="false"
            class="hidden md:inline-block px-2 py-1 border rounded"
          >
            System Fonts
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <nav data-variant="main">
      <ul class="cluster" style="--region-space: 1.5rem;" role="list">
        {% for item in navigation.top %}
          <li>
            <a
              href="{{ item.url }}"
              data-variant="naked"
              {% if item.url==url %}aria-current="page"{% endif %}
            >
              {{ item.text }}
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
